OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis charters ships  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto ensure Christmas stock  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Farrives                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, John Lewis is chartering a fleet of    
OL,6, extra ships, along with a number of    
OL,7, other businesses, to make sure it has  
OL,8, Christmas stock on time.               
OL,10,FRetailers have been grappling with a   
OL,11,Fhost of supply chain problems from     
OL,12,Fdriver shortages to shipping delays.   
OL,14,FJohn Lewis chair Sharon White said the 
OL,15,Fbusiness was throwing everything at the
OL,16,Fissues to make sure Christmas would not
OL,17,Fbe disrupted.                          
OL,19,FThe retailer recorded a pre-tax loss of
OL,20,F#29m for the six months to 31 July.    
